Peterborough Beats Huddersfield 3-0 to Return to Soccer’s Championship

-- B y   J a m e s   C o n e
-- 
2011-05-29T15:57:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-29/peterborough-beats-huddersfield-3-0-to-return-to-soccer-s-championship.html
Peterborough defeated Huddersfield 3-
0 in today’s League One playoff final to return to English
soccer’s second-tier Championship at the first attempt.  Peterborough got goals from Tommy Rowe, Craig Mackail-Smith
and Grant McCann in the final 12 minutes at Old Trafford in
Manchester today.   Brighton and Southampton already secured spots in the
Championship next season after finishing first and second
respectively in League One.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Cone at 
 jcone@bloomberg.net  